-- 6. Even Tone Correcting Serum
UPDATE products SET
  image_url = '/images/products/skinbetter/even-tone.jpg',
  price = 165.00,
  size = '50ml / 1.7 fl oz',
  description = 'Even Tone Correcting Serum is a multi-pathway brightening treatment by skinbetter science that targets visible discoloration, dark spots, melasma maintenance, and overall dullness. The formula uses arbutin, niacinamide, hexylresorcinol, and phytic acid to interrupt melanin production at multiple stages—a comprehensive approach that delivers visible brightening without the irritation of hydroquinone. Available at RELUXE Med Spa in Westfield and Carmel, Indiana.

Pigmentation is one of the most common concerns our Hamilton County patients bring to RELUXE, and Even Tone is a cornerstone of our at-home pigment protocols. Indiana''s seasonal UV exposure—especially the strong summer sun—can trigger and worsen melasma, sun spots, and post-inflammatory hyperpigmentation. Even Tone provides daily pigment suppression that compounds over time, especially when paired with consistent mineral SPF and periodic in-clinic treatments like IPL, chemical peels, or laser resurfacing. The serum layers beautifully under other skinbetter products and can be used alongside AlphaRet for a complete evening anti-aging + brightening routine.',
  faq = '[{"q":"How long until I see brightening results?","a":"Most patients notice visible improvement in overall radiance within 2-3 weeks. Significant reduction in dark spots and discoloration typically occurs at the 6-8 week mark with consistent daily use."},{"q":"Is Even Tone safe for melasma patients?","a":"Yes—it''s specifically designed for melasma maintenance. The multi-pathway formula avoids hydroquinone while still delivering meaningful pigment correction. Pair with daily mineral SPF and periodic in-clinic treatments at RELUXE for best results."},{"q":"Can I layer Even Tone with AlphaRet?","a":"Yes. Apply Even Tone first, allow it to absorb, then apply AlphaRet Overnight Cream. This combination addresses both pigmentation and texture simultaneously—it''s one of the most effective evening protocols our RELUXE clinicians recommend."},{"q":"Where can I get melasma treatment near me in Hamilton County?","a":"RELUXE Med Spa offers comprehensive melasma management at both our Westfield and Carmel locations. Even Tone is part of our at-home melasma protocol, paired with mineral SPF, in-clinic IPL, chemical peels, and SkinCeuticals Discoloration Defense for a multi-product approach."}]'::JSONB,
  staff_picks = '{"westfield":"Our Westfield team''s top pick for pigment-prone patients. Even Tone + daily mineral SPF + periodic IPL at RELUXE is the gold-standard melasma protocol across Hamilton County.","carmel":"Melasma-friendly maintenance that compounds over time. The Carmel team layers it under AlphaRet for a one-two punch of brightening and anti-aging that patients see and feel."}'::JSONB,
  related_services = ARRAY['ipl-photofacial', 'chemical-peels', 'laser-resurfacing']
WHERE slug = 'even-tone-correcting-serum';


