-- 6. Glycolic 10 Renew Overnight
UPDATE products SET
  image_url = '/images/products/skinceuticals/glycolic.jpg',
  price = 80.00,
  size = '50ml / 1.7 fl oz',
  description = 'Glycolic 10 Renew Overnight is a night treatment by SkinCeuticals that uses 10% glycolic acid in a time-release formula to refine skin texture, reduce roughness, and improve radiance while you sleep. Unlike leave-on peels that can irritate, the sustained-release technology delivers glycolic acid gradually throughout the night, minimizing irritation while maximizing the exfoliating and brightening benefits. A soothing complex buffers the acid for comfortable nightly use. Available exclusively at RELUXE Med Spa in Westfield and Carmel, Indiana.

Glycolic acid is the smallest alpha hydroxy acid molecule, allowing it to penetrate effectively and dissolve the bonds between dead skin cells that cause dullness, roughness, and uneven texture. Glycolic 10 Renew Overnight harnesses this power in a gentle nightly format that''s ideal for patients who can''t tolerate retinoids or want to add an exfoliating step to complement their retinoid routine. Indiana''s seasonal dryness—especially in winter—can cause surface buildup that makes skin look dull and rough. This treatment addresses that directly, revealing smoother, brighter skin by morning. Our RELUXE clinicians often recommend it as an alternative evening active for patients who experience too much irritation from retinoids, or as a 2-3 times per week addition to an AlphaRet or tretinoin routine.',
  faq = '[{"q":"Can I use Glycolic 10 with a retinoid like AlphaRet?","a":"Yes, but on alternate nights. Use Glycolic 10 Renew Overnight 2-3 times per week and your retinoid on the other nights. Your RELUXE provider in Westfield or Carmel can help build the ideal schedule for your skin."},{"q":"Is this gentler than an in-clinic chemical peel?","a":"Yes. Glycolic 10 Renew Overnight uses time-release technology that delivers glycolic acid gradually, plus a built-in soothing complex. It provides consistent, gentle exfoliation rather than the concentrated single-session approach of an in-clinic peel. Both have their place—talk to your RELUXE provider about the right combination."},{"q":"How quickly will I see smoother skin?","a":"Most patients notice smoother texture and improved radiance within 1-2 weeks of consistent use. Start 2-3 times per week and increase to nightly as tolerated."},{"q":"Who is this best for?","a":"Patients with dull, rough-textured skin who want gentle nightly exfoliation. It''s also excellent for patients who can''t tolerate retinoids, or as a complement to retinoid therapy on alternating nights. Especially popular among our Hamilton County patients during Indiana''s dry winter months."}]'::JSONB,
  staff_picks = '{"westfield":"Our Westfield team''s retinoid alternative for sensitive patients. Glycolic 10 delivers nightly texture refinement without the irritation—perfect for patients easing into an active skincare routine.","carmel":"The Carmel team loves pairing Glycolic 10 with AlphaRet on alternating nights. Two different exfoliation pathways, maximum smoothing, and the time-release formula keeps irritation minimal even in Indiana''s dry winters."}'::JSONB,
  related_services = ARRAY['chemical-peels', 'microneedling']
WHERE slug = 'glycolic-10-renew-overnight';


