  image_url = '/images/products/universkin/p-serum.png',
  price = 165.00,
  size = '30ml / 1 fl oz',
  description = 'P Serum + Madecassoside (MAD) is a personalized serum by Universkin that soothes, calms, and repairs reactive and sensitive skin using provider-selected madecassoside concentration. Derived from Centella asiatica (tiger grass), madecassoside is a powerful anti-inflammatory and wound-healing compound that promotes collagen synthesis, reduces redness, and strengthens the skin barrier. It''s the active of choice for chronically sensitive skin and post-procedure recovery. Available exclusively at RELUXE Med Spa in Westfield and Carmel, Indiana.

Sensitive skin isn''t just uncomfortable—it limits what treatments and products you can use. Madecassoside addresses the root cause of sensitivity by repairing the skin barrier and calming the inflammatory cascade that triggers redness, stinging, and reactivity. For our Hamilton County patients, it''s especially valuable during Indiana''s harsh seasonal transitions when cold, dry winter air followed by humid summer heat can trigger sensitivity flares. Your RELUXE provider can use madecassoside as a standalone calming active or combine it with gentle anti-aging ingredients like peptides and niacinamide to build a multi-benefit formula that improves your skin without provoking it.',
  faq = '[{"q":"What is madecassoside and how does it help sensitive skin?","a":"Madecassoside is a compound derived from Centella asiatica (tiger grass) with powerful anti-inflammatory and wound-healing properties. It calms redness, promotes collagen synthesis, and strengthens the skin barrier—addressing the root cause of chronic sensitivity rather than just masking symptoms."},{"q":"Can I use this after procedures at RELUXE?","a":"Yes—madecassoside is excellent for post-procedure recovery. It promotes healing, reduces inflammation, and supports barrier repair. Your provider may include it in your Universkin formula during the recovery phase after microneedling or laser treatments."},{"q":"Is this the same as Centella asiatica in Korean skincare?","a":"Madecassoside is the most potent active compound extracted from Centella asiatica. While many K-beauty products use Centella broadly, Universkin delivers the specific active compound at a clinical concentration customized to your skin''s needs."},{"q":"Where can I get treatment for sensitive skin near me in Indiana?","a":"RELUXE Med Spa in Westfield and Carmel specializes in managing sensitive and reactive skin. Universkin P Serum + Madecassoside is part of our calming skincare protocol, often combined with Hydrinity recovery products and gentle in-clinic treatments."}]'::JSONB,
  staff_picks = '{"westfield":"Our Westfield team''s go-to for chronically sensitive patients. Madecassoside repairs the barrier and calms reactivity from the inside out—especially valuable during Indiana''s harsh seasonal swings across Hamilton County.","carmel":"The Carmel team blends madecassoside with niacinamide for patients who want anti-aging benefits without triggering their sensitivity. It''s the gentlest path to better skin for reactive Hamilton County complexions."}'::JSONB,
